referenceFunction.name: electricity, low voltage, production UCTE, at grid
referenceFunction.localName: Strom, Niederspannung, Produktion UCTE, ab Netz
referenceFunction.generalComment: This dataset describes the transformation medium to low voltage, the distribution of electricity at low voltage. Included are electricity losses and direct SF6-emissions to air.

geography.text: The calculation of total specific losses are based on national data. Specific infrastructure demand is based on Swiss data. Specific SF6-Emissions (percentage of SF6 stock) are mainly based on German data.

technology.text: Average technology used to distribute electricity. Includes underground and overhead lines, as well as air- and SF6-insulated medium-to-low voltage switching stations

timePeriod.text: Data on SF6 emissions and electricity consumption are for 2000

representativeness.extrapolations: Attribution of total losses to losses on low voltage level are based on assumptions.

source.additionalAuthors: Tuchschmid, M., Faist Emmenegger, M.,Bauer, C., Dones, R.
source.title: Strommix und Stromnetz
source.titleOfAnthology: Sachbilanzen von Energiesystemen. Final report No. 6 ecoinvent data v2.0
